import { green, gold } from '@ant-design/colors';
export const palette = {
  black: "#1d1d1d",
  white: "#ffffff",
  offWhite: "#e6e6e6",
  orange: "#FBA928",
  orangeDarker: "#EB9918",
  lightGrey: "#939AA4",
  lighterGrey: "#CDD4DA",
  angry: "#dd3333",
  blue: "#0c7fc7",
  default: "#3e3e3e",
  defaultDarker: "#363535"
}
